title: Tin Foil Hat #36: Chaos Magic with Gordon White
description:
Thank you for tuning into another fun festive episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. Today, Ryan and Sam, welcome Chaos Magician Gordon White to the show. On this episode we discuss....
1) Sam Tripoli's appearance at the Punchlinephilly.com/SamTripoli
2)Chaos Magic
3)Rune Soup
4)Graham Hancock
5)Nuclear War on Mars
6)Alien Disclosure
7)The Queen of England
8) We read your iTunes reviews
